76561198092065417,Recommended,429600,24630422,"Posted: 31 July, 2016",all,SoS (Piney),"I haven't written many reviews lately on HOGs because the majority of them seem to be...well...rehashes on every other one.  This one is rather good however.  It still keeps all the same commonalities of HOGs (hidden object puzzles, casual pick and choose puzzles, color matching, tile puzzles), but it actually has fairly good voice acting, better than average animation for a HOG, and a music loop that suits the mood (although you will likely get tired of it).  Not very challenging, but decent.  Get it on sale.  Easy achievements, easy to beat, relatively low replay value."
